{"tid":2162185,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白羅斯總統：通過修憲公投後　重新選舉及交出權力","createTime":"2020-08-18T03:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T04:02:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c2a9160d906c54f0a075acda9aeec7f0fb5a0ce","tid":2162185,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:52:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544313-20200818.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544313-20200818.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF0ZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=189de915\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544313-20200818.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f142dce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544313-20200818.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n白羅斯的反政府示威持續。總統盧卡申科被指立場軟化，他表示，準備在通過修憲公投之後，重新舉行選舉，交出權力。但他強調，不會屈服於壓力及街頭示威。<br />\n<br />\n有分析認為，盧卡申科希望盡快平息民憤，但亦有分析指他希望藉此拖延時間。<br />\n<br />\n盧卡申科在較早前參觀一間工廠，向工人發表措辭強硬的演說，表示政府已舉行選舉，除非自己被殺，否則不會重選。不過，現場有工人向他喝倒采，要求他下台，盧卡申科提早離開。<br />\n<br />\n首都明斯克在星期日繼續有反政府示威，據報有10萬人參與，是白俄羅斯獨立後規模最大的示威，多個行業有工人罷工，包括國營電視台員工。"},{"pid":"8f77e8ca9146209102e7729e176a8b2053bc1bdf","tid":2162185,"uid":256837,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"淋病：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01bdd089b890cdec89855c173d94a1942b8e4873","tid":2162185,"uid":29188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:58:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544313-20200818.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544313-20200818.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF0ZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=189de915\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih